內的世界各國互相傳播，並分享高速燒屍經驗。新型冠狀國希望美國能摒棄偏見，全面正確看待有關問題，客觀公正看待新型冠狀國，多為世界衛生組織貢獻賄款。"},{"pid":"9e042d1e86ccdda6ae226a701809f32bf0fe18ac","tid":1928476,"uid":85190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T12:15:25.000Z","msg":"就算WHO有證據 譚Nigger都唔會比佢出街<br />\n大陸更加會張佢消滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b08c5b8f88a3600f7d70ee104bf3c2d1003935e","tid":1928476,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T12:16:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5533c20ec6e96527d90fed0e704944c13d5936aa","tid":1928476,"uid":298796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T12:35:09.000Z","msg":"難得 南美文學家有咁高道德情操"},{"pid":"f4067961eb2ac950d608c8e9ccfc0507be443a32","tid":1928476,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}